name: Mailbox Mover
overview:
Mailbox Mover copies consumer email from one email account to another for $7.

For example, if someone is leaving college and wants to keep his or her old email, Mailbox Mover can interface with any IMAP server and help keep those old messages around forever. Or if someone is changing from an old webmail account with a clever username to a new gmail account with a professional address, Mailbox Mover, once again, can help.

The service is simple. Enter your old and new email addresses, login information, and choose how you want folders to be mapped. Pay with Google Checkout, and sit back and relax while your old email is copied to your new address.
